<!---

File		: Viewer3DComponent.mxml
Module		: 3DViewer
Developer(s): Jayakrishnan R, Arun V
Reviewer(s)	: Pradeesh,Remya T

Viewer3DComponent.mxml is the main 3Dviewer component adding to the main application.
In this componet we adding the 3Dviewer library and pop-out button.

-->

<s:BorderContainer xmlns:fx="http://ns.adobe.com/mxml/2009"
				   xmlns:s="library://ns.adobe.com/flex/spark"
				   xmlns:mx="library://ns.adobe.com/flex/mx"
				   width="100%"
				   height="100%"
				   backgroundAlpha="0"
				   borderAlpha="0"
				   borderStyle="solid"
				   creationComplete="init()"
				   xmlns:local="*"
				   enabled="{ClassroomContext.IS_3D_ENABLED}">
	<fx:Script source="FileHandler3D.as"/>
	<fx:Script source="Viewer3DComponentHandler.as"/>
	<!-- Adding the 3Dviewer library-->
	<local:Viewer3DSWC id="viewer3DSWC"
					   initialize="viewer3DSWC_initializeHandler(event)"/>
	
</s:BorderContainer>
